OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy in the evening with rain over
OL,7,FShetland clearing to the north, and
OL,8,Fshowers gradually easing over Orkney.
OL,9,FLargely dry overnight with just the
OL,10,Fodd light shower possible. Some mist
OL,11,For fog patches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRather cloudy, some fog
OL,14,Fpatches over Shetland, but with some
OL,15,Fsunny intervals breaking through. A
OL,16,Ffew light showers, then some rain in
OL,17,Fthe evening, with moderate southeast
OL,18,Fbreezes developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
