OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDull
OL,6,Fon Tuesday with haar and chance of
OL,7,Frain. Bright spells and a few showers
OL,8,Fon Wednesday. Brighter with sunny
OL,9,Fintervals and one or two showers on
OL,10,FThursday.
